        "description": {
          "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"1\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Innate Spellcasting.</span></span> <p>The unfinished's innate spellcasting ability is Charisma (spell save DC <span class=\"rd__dc\">16</span>, [[/r 1d20+8]]{+8} to hit with spell attacks). The unfinished can innately cast the following spells, requiring no material components:</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><ul class=\"rd__list rd__list-hang-notitle\"><li class=\"rd__li  rd__li-spell\"><p>At will: @UUID[Actor.UxXamrxbMOLoPV9y.Item.XCzlGxorTQHUus2Q]</p></li><li class=\"rd__li  rd__li-spell\"><p>3/day each: @UUID[Actor.UxXamrxbMOLoPV9y.Item.cM60xxbprCI68PSu]{arcane hand} (9th-level), @UUID[Actor.UxXamrxbMOLoPV9y.Item.4PSgQGeZgPTUXbP2]</p></li></ul></div><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>",
